{{Current wildfire}} {{Use mdy dates|date=September 2018}}
{{Infobox wildfire | title = 2018 Utah wildfires | image = | caption = | reference = | coordinates = | total_area = | total_fires = | date = June, 2018 – | buildings = | fatalities = | is_season = yes | year = 2018 | season_name = Utah wildfires }}
The 2018 wildfire season in Utah began around June, 2018.
Fires included: * [[Trail Mountain Fire]] (June 6–) * [[West Valley Fire]] (June 27–August 7) * [[Dollar Ridge Fire]] (July 1–) * [[Pole Creek Fire (2018)|Pole Creek Fire]] (September 6–)
