iemy.pl/kultura/od-pol-roku-kilar-zmagal-sie-z-nowotworem/ |newspaper=Tygodnik Idziemy |location= |publisher= |accessdate=13 January 2013}}</ref> *[[2014]] &ndash; [[Hari Harilela]], Indian-Hong Kong businessman and philanthropist (b. 1922) * 2014 &ndash; [[Juanito Remulla, Sr.]], Filipino lawyer and politician, [[Governor of Cavite]] (b. 1933) *[[2015]] &ndash; [[Om Prakash Malhotra]], Indian general and politician, 25th [[List of governors of Punjab (India)|Governor of Punjab]] (b. 1922) * 2015 &ndash; [[Pavel Srníček]], Czech footballer and coach (b. 1968) *[[2016]] &ndash; [[Keion Carpenter]], American football defensive back (b. 1977) * 2016 &ndash; [[LaVell Edwards]], American football head coach (b. 1930) <!-- Do not add people without Wikipedia articles to this list. Do not trust “this year in history” websites for accurate date information. Do not link multiple occurrences of the same year, just link the first occurrence. -->
